data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious 6-bed, 4.5-bath residence offers large rooms throughout. The first floor boasts a versatile layout, featuring a bedroom with connecting bath, perfect for guests/private retreat. The expansive flex area can be tailored to your lifestyle: A formal living/dining space, or game room for entertainment. The heart of the home resides on the first floor, where the kitchen seamlessly connects to the family room, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is well-appointed, & a large walk-in pantry ensures ample storage. 1/2 bath adds to the functionality of this level. Step outside to a delightful screened-in porch, offering a serene space to relax surrounded by nature. Ascending to the second floor, you'll find a generously sized loft area. The remaining five bedrooms provide plenty of room. Roof 6 yrs old, A/C 1 yr old. & solar panels make this home energy efficient. Special Financing Incentives available for this home from SIRVA Mortgage.
